{"tid":2392720,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"李嘉誠向醫管局全體人員送心意卡 可換200蚊現金券","createTime":"2021-02-03T03:34:35.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-03T14:12:01.000Z","uid":184679,"like":59,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"39b6d37bd0dd304b83cf0f275042f837fc232d8c","tid":2392720,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T03:34:35.000Z","msg":"李嘉誠基金會在社交媒體表示，立春之日，李嘉誠給香港醫護送上春天的禮物，向醫管局全體9.7萬人員送上心意卡。手持心意卡，由2月8日至5月31日，即可在全港百佳店舖換取及使用200元現金券。<br />\n<br />\n心意卡寫上:「謝謝您們一直守護香港人的健康，我與全港市民一樣，內心都為您們鼓掌。一點心意，與您共勉。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.hkej.com/hkej/images/2021/02/03/2704447_35555f9a9c725d2ab5e5515045a069ea.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.hkej.com%2Fhkej%2Fimages%2F2021%2F02%2F03%2F2704447_35555f9a9c725d2ab5e5515045a069ea.jpg&h=0d9edddd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2704447/李嘉誠向醫管局全體人員送心意卡\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Flanding%2FmobArticle2%2Fid%2F2704447%2F%E6%9D%8E%E5%98%89%E8%AA%A0%E5%90%91%E9%86%AB%E7%AE%A1%E5%B1%80%E5%85%A8%E9%AB%94%E4%BA%BA%E5%93%A1%E9%80%81%E5%BF%83%E6%84%8F%E5%8D%A1&d=FM8PVMPbIH5fyb1BVmxPrY6aL69TDc1SPHZju%2B%2BXLiQ%3D&h=f0f85039\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2704447/李嘉誠向醫管局全體人員送心意卡</a>"},{"pid":"6eb6503db15a01308bedabf38e89a720b34e4fbd","tid":2392720,"uid":230104,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T03:35:50.000Z","msg":"但同時承諾供養袁志偉、黃淑明、李寶安"},{"pid":"3aa99a95a9d70db68db2b93eda905a31e429d756","tid":2392720,"uid":51271,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T03:36:04.000Z","msg":"咦，會唔會引起咖啡店注意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d9a0225da01dea78e3ffa58e67e50034eff39a6","tid":2392720,"uid":301820,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T03:36:52.000Z","msg":"誠哥去英國<br />\n<br />\n跟機保平安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good